                           <ab type="conservation">Medium dark brown papyrus of good quality; broken off at the left side; regularly cut at the top, right and bottom, the margins are preserved at top, right and bottom; the papyrus has suffered damage, lacunae in several parts, especially at the right side. There is a horizontal kollesis c.a. 3 cm from the top edge; there are some dark blots of dirt on verso.</ab>
